OL,3,CTony Hudgell honoured by Evelina in
OL,4,Cthanks for fundraising efforts
OL,6,FA nine-year-old boy who raised #1.8
OL,7,Fmillion for charity has said he is "so
OL,8,Fhappy and proud" to be honoured by the
OL,9,Fhospital that saved his life.
OL,11,FTony Hudgell, from West Malling in
OL,12,FKent, was surprised on Thursday with a
OL,13,Fceiling tile depicting him as an
OL,14,Fastronaut in a new space-themed unit
OL,15,Fat Evelina London Children's Hospital
OL,16,F` which #500,000 of his fundraising
OL,17,Fhas gone towards.
