OL,3,CTony Hudgell honoured by Evelina in
OL,4,Cthanks for fundraising efforts
OL,6,FThe tile, which shows Tony with his
OL,7,Fcrutches, prosthetic legs and a name
OL,8,Fbadge, will serve as an "everlasting
OL,9,Flegacy" of his support for the new
OL,10,FChildren's Day Surgery Unit, which
OL,11,Fopened to patients in July 2023.
OL,13,FTony has received specialist and life-
OL,14,Fsaving treatment at the children's
OL,15,Fhospital since he was a baby.
