OL,3,CTony Hudgell honoured by Evelina in
OL,4,Cthanks for fundraising efforts
OL,6,FHe was just 41 days old when he was
OL,7,Fassaulted by his birth parents, an
OL,8,Fattack which caused multiple fractures
OL,9,Fand dislocations, and blunt trauma to
OL,10,Fthe face, leading to organ failure,
OL,11,Ftoxic shock and sepsis.
OL,13,FTony was left untreated and in agony
OL,14,Ffor 10 days and because of the extent
OL,15,Fof his injuries both his legs had to
OL,16,Fbe amputated.
OL,18,FJody Simpson and her partner Anthony
OL,19,FSmith were jailed for 10 years in 2018.
