OL,3,CTony Hudgell honoured by Evelina in
OL,4,Cthanks for fundraising efforts
OL,6,FPaula and Mark Hudgell fostered Tony
OL,7,Fwhen he was six weeks old and adopted
OL,8,Fhim at 17 months in 2016.
OL,10,FAt the age of five, Tony challenged
OL,11,Fhimself to walk every day in June to
OL,12,Fraise money for Evelina London
OL,13,FChildren's Charity with an initial
OL,14,Ftarget of #509 and four years later,
OL,15,Fhe is the charity's biggest fundraiser
OL,16,Fto date.
