OL,3,CTony Hudgell honoured by Evelina in
OL,4,Cthanks for fundraising efforts
OL,6,FTo thank him for his efforts, Tony and
OL,7,FPaula were given a tour of the new
OL,8,Fouter-space themed unit, which is
OL,9,Fequipped with two operating theatres
OL,10,Fto help treat up to an additional
OL,11,F2,300 children every year.
OL,13,FDuring the tour, Tony was asked to
OL,14,Flook up and was thrilled to see
OL,15,Fhimself portrayed as an astronaut on
OL,16,Fthe ceiling tile, saying: "I'm so
OL,17,Fhappy and proud."
