OL,3,CTony Hudgell honoured by Evelina in
OL,4,Cthanks for fundraising efforts
OL,6,FMs Hudgell, 56, told the PA news
OL,7,Fagency: "It's just lovely that he's
OL,8,Fpart of that building in an
OL,9,Feverlasting legacy there and I'm so
OL,10,Fproud.
OL,12,F"You always want to help the hospital
OL,13,Fthat helped your child ` the hospital
OL,14,Fis so important to us and it saved his
OL,15,Flife.
OL,17,F"It still seems surreal that he raised
OL,18,Fthat amount of money and it's just
OL,19,Fwonderful to be able to give back."
