OL,6,FTony was also gifted a souvenir
OL,7,Fversion of the tile to take home with
OL,8,Fhim, as well as an engraved brick from
OL,9,Fthe foundations of the building.
OL,11,FThe visit also gave Tony the chance to
OL,12,Fbe reunited with his surgeon, Michail
OL,13,FKokkinakis, who said the youngster's
OL,14,Ffundraising efforts were "out-of-this-
OL,15,Fworld".
