OL,3,CTony Hudgell honoured by Evelina in
OL,4,Cthanks for fundraising efforts
OL,6,FHe said: "His (Tony's) out-of-this-
OL,7,Fworld fundraising continues to make a
OL,8,Fpositive difference to the children we
OL,9,Fcare for at Evelina London and thanks
OL,10,Fto his determination, we can bring
OL,11,Fsmiles to the faces of anxious
OL,12,Fchildren and hope to worried families."
OL,14,FSupported by Tony's fundraising, the
OL,15,Fnew unit has created extra capacity to
OL,16,Ftreat children with more complex
OL,17,Fconditions and since opening, more
OL,18,Fthan 1,180 children and their families
OL,19,Fhave been treated there.
